  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>You dark energy increases, allowing you to cast more powerful graveknight spells. You gain a 1st-rank spell slot that can be used to cast spells of your graveknight curse's tradition. <span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">Each time you gain a spell slot of a new rank from the graveknight archetype, add a spell of that rank or lower to your repertoire. You are a bounded spellcaster. Each time you lose spell slots of a particular rank, remove those spells from your repertoire. At 6th level, you gain a 2nd-rank spell, and at 8th level, you replace your 1st-rank spell slot with a 3rd-rank spell slot.</span></p>"
